  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/880310/extras/894a3dfbed1fde6a3605605d63384eb2.webp?t=1643377493\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>Pro Microphone is an app for all who want to be heard - from karaoke adorers to professional singers.<br>Create new hits by using the power of our tools and your own voice!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/880310/extras/8c05fb60b5c9176fb07cb275309b1a88.avif?t=1643377493\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIGHLIGHTS</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sound recording<br></li><li>Loop management system<br></li><li>Various backing tracks</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFERENT TYPES OF MICROPHONES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stage Microphone<br></li><li>Simple Dynamic Microphone<br></li><li>Tube Microphone<br></li><li>Studio Microphone<br></li><li>Condenser Microphone<br></li><li>Retro Microphone</li></ul>Each has its unique sounding and parameters — it allows you to find the one that suits your voice best.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/880310/extras/6e8c01b7f6748a4261ee96f1c28499f8.avif?t=1643377493\" width=600 height=294 /></span><br>Pro Microphone is the most suitable tool for rehearsal or singing exercises. Impress everyone with your vocals!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/880310/extras/b3c02d5f0c48939f0a8c6e9b878332ef.webp?t=1643377493\" width=600 height=55 /></span>",
